# Project Structure Planning Example
# This demonstrates how to plan a project structure using treex draw

my-webapp/ Modern Web Application
my-webapp/.github/ GitHub configuration
my-webapp/.github/workflows/ CI/CD pipelines
my-webapp/.github/workflows/test.yml Run tests on PR
my-webapp/.github/workflows/deploy.yml Deploy to production

my-webapp/src/ Source code
my-webapp/src/components/ React components
my-webapp/src/components/common/ Shared components
my-webapp/src/components/common/Button/ Button component
my-webapp/src/components/common/Modal/ Modal dialog component
my-webapp/src/components/features/ Feature-specific components
my-webapp/src/components/features/Auth/ Authentication components
my-webapp/src/components/features/Dashboard/ Dashboard components

my-webapp/src/api/ API integration layer
my-webapp/src/api/client.ts API client configuration
my-webapp/src/api/endpoints/ API endpoint definitions
my-webapp/src/api/endpoints/auth.ts Authentication endpoints
my-webapp/src/api/endpoints/users.ts User management endpoints

my-webapp/src/hooks/ Custom React hooks
my-webapp/src/hooks/useAuth.ts Authentication hook
my-webapp/src/hooks/useApi.ts Generic API hook

my-webapp/src/utils/ Utility functions
my-webapp/src/utils/validation.ts Form validation helpers
my-webapp/src/utils/formatting.ts Data formatting utilities

my-webapp/tests/ Test files
my-webapp/tests/unit/ Unit tests
my-webapp/tests/integration/ Integration tests
my-webapp/tests/e2e/ End-to-end tests

my-webapp/docs/ Documentation
my-webapp/docs/api/ API documentation
my-webapp/docs/guides/ User guides
my-webapp/docs/architecture/ Architecture decisions

my-webapp/scripts/ Build and utility scripts
my-webapp/scripts/setup.sh Initial setup script
my-webapp/scripts/deploy.sh Deployment script

my-webapp/config/ Configuration files
my-webapp/config/webpack/ Webpack configurations
my-webapp/config/jest/ Jest test configuration